name: Garage Door and Gate Solutions
overview:
Garage Door & Gate Solutions Pty Ltd began life in 1996. The company principal, Frank Van Den Broek, purchased assets and re-employed a number of staff from the business previously known as A&R Doors, which was established in 1976, in Clayton Victoria. In 1996 the business operated from a 5,000 square foot factory in Urban Street Braeside. In mid 2004, the business moved to an 11,000 square foot factory at 23 Canterbury Road Braeside. Since 1996, the business has enjoyed strong growth, and remains focused on its goal of striving to be the “finest provider of high quality, great value packages of product and service in the garage door industry in Victoria “.

Today there is close to 100,000 homes across Melbourne with a garage door manufactured, installed or serviced by the dedicated staff from A&R Doors and now Garage Door & Gate Solutions.

The proprietors of Garage Door & Gate Solutions Pty Ltd, husband and wife team Frank and Trish Van Den Broek, have been in the garage door industry since 1977, having previously operated another successful garage door business in Melbourne.

Garage Door & Gate Solutions Pty Ltd has been a member of International Door Association since 1998.
